item.description: Making this a regular thing! We meet at the Rite Aid parking lot and walking down to At least Bridge street, maybe even the Verizon center if it's really nice. Come practice some good, formal, on-leash walks with your best friends and their owners!
item.how_to_find_us: Look for my blue Ford Escort Wagon near the Rite aid Sign. Bella is also a dead giveaway.
